{"tid":2310214,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李臻，柒婆嫌你mild呀！- 高慧然","createTime":"2020-12-03T05:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T07:03:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"486274db762ca7ef023dbc6a974051b8cf8bd6a3","tid":2310214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201203/RFRUHHRWJBDEFDWIUHY7FCJI4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201203%2FRFRUHHRWJBDEFDWIUHY7FCJI4Q%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=42b6a269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201203%2FRFRUHHRWJBDEFDWIUHY7FCJI4Q%2F&h=bca3be7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201203/RFRUHHRWJBDEFDWIUHY7FCJI4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李臻，柒婆嫌你mild呀！- 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IqXjMT4CI7YzgKvvnoi2gXBYehA=/1242x719/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A7T62AATNVDPXP46NFMBMROEBI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIqXjMT4CI7YzgKvvnoi2gXBYehA%3D%2F1242x719%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA7T62AATNVDPXP46NFMBMROEBI.png&h=9deb0654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞部新晉高層李臻訪問柒婆，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李臻固然卑賤，毫無新聞從業者的風骨，柒婆卻也不要以為罵兩句「合作」與「配合」就可以掩蓋扼殺新聞自由、言論自由的罪行。不過是幾天之前，在趕絕異議聲的立法會，對着一群完全無視她存在、或睡覺、或買蟹、或打機的議員，柒婆讀完所謂的施政報告，享受完一言堂的快樂之後，樂不可支地宣稱她得到了尊重。此時此刻，面對李臻，在絕對安全的情況下，竟挑剔問題不夠尖銳。哈哈哈！如果多來幾個不同媒體的記者，任由他們提問，問題不經事先篩選，柒婆你敢面對鏡頭嗎？如果問題是：「你為甚麼從來不說人話？是不會說人話，還是已經忘記了自己是個人？」「去太子站獻花犯法嗎？」「見到香港警隊今日的形象，你內心可有羞愧？」「可以談談你對721的睇法嗎？」「香港人為你打了負分，你為甚麼還厚着臉皮不走？」「如果有機會見到周梓樂的父母，你想對他們說些甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n一個人，要無恥到甚麼程度，才會做婊子立牌坊，在獨裁之下，教傳媒假扮尖銳。"},{"pid":"082f61e4f65b187165ac1741ce7eb15201b89137","tid":2310214,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"現代太監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5779c15a5c38583ffc487c28bf968b63e7e25af","tid":2310214,"uid":188805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"個嘻嘻帶有幾分太監色彩"},{"pid":"dfcc3c98761442a13151bd36aaf88ac3d25aa171","tid":2310214,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"又要人做太監，又嫌人無jer，呢個女人真係難服侍。"},{"pid":"be921a10c6e0ac61141574d064e38bbc1b8bbbc9","tid":2310214,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"今晚會硬淨d hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}